						<div class="postbody">It seems to run on 2.2.3 if I switch to &quot;Old PPU&quot;.<br /><br />The new PPU is supposed to be much more accurate, but I'm not sure specifically in what ways.<br /><br />The default setting is old PPU, but I think it's mainly that way to provide support for legacy TAS etc. that relies on its behaviour. If you're trying to develop new software, you would probably want to use new PPU.</div>

